sub_title: Climate Impact Scientist at Lobelia Earth
summary:
Spatial data scientist helping businesses quantify and assess water, environmental and climate-related risks using geospatial data.

Main fields of expertise: Physical climate risk (drought floods) | Water vulnerability assessment | Agricultural monitoring | Spatiotemporal analysis of the environment
